ORDER
The defendant’s motion to supplement the record on appeal with the transcript of a hearing on pre-trial motions is granted.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts, II, Atty. Gen., Stephan Lichatin III, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Janice M. Weisfeld, Asst. Public Defender, for defendant.

STATE v. Harvey BAKER.
